u terhadap penyebab kegagalan atau keterbatasan dalam pelaksanaan upaya intervensi yang sudah atau sedang dilakukan. Sebagai contoh, apabila penyelenggaraan hari menanam pohon nasional hanya memberikan sedikit hasil nyata di lapangan walaupun meskipun telah dilakukan selama beberapa dekade, kajian yang dilakukan seharusnya dapat memberi penjelasan mengapa hal ini terjadi.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "92c5470b-f65e-4102-961d-91e1ff0c098d": {"__data__": {"id_": "92c5470b-f65e-4102-961d-91e1ff0c098d", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/id/resources/grey-literature/pedoman-metode-evaluasi-kesempatan-restorasi-mekar", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Pedoman Metode Evaluasi Kesempatan Restorasi (MEKAR)", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/id/resources/grey-literature/pedoman-metode-evaluasi-kesempatan-restorasi-mekar", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "69309cb7562cfdecfc4f9f70d6b162ab1dae9efcd72c0029465935948e40e77e"}, "2": {"node_id": "bdd9c616-54b7-4e7d-a340-b7a2591741ce", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/id/resources/grey-literature/pedoman-metode-evaluasi-kesempatan-restorasi-mekar", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "d9ace612f8722ba90d7b44adc0486e4029b800f7d767995bf5d99f0489374391"}, "3": {"node_id": "3492e565-6ca0-4d15-aad8-7423937f2c04", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_U