 inheren dapat dipasarkan), serta mendorong pengembangan strategi restorasi yang yang paling menarik secara komersial dengan mengabaikan nilai-nilai yang tidak terkait dengan pasar. Namun kemungkinan terjadinya hal seperti ini kecil dengan analisis yang dirancang dan digunakan dengan tepat.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "0df684ce-fa57-483e-ab1c-cdd610a4163b": {"__data__": {"id_": "0df684ce-fa57-483e-ab1c-cdd610a4163b", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/id/resources/grey-literature/pedoman-metode-evaluasi-kesempatan-restorasi-mekar", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Pedoman Metode Evaluasi Kesempatan Restorasi (MEKAR)", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/id/resources/grey-literature/pedoman-metode-evaluasi-kesempatan-restorasi-mekar", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "b6f6272b01e1257dfd9ce517c44e9a0b1c43208359de3f49d243f9af29cb5643"}, "2": {"node_id": "b0df1aab-4f9d-4d34-841b-a3f14c4c262a", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/id/resources/grey-literature/pedoman-metode-evaluasi-kesempatan-restorasi-mekar", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "331b57b22edd3560b4e0f73d5c43f4d4dae39e8eafe6dc0456fc3b9ea7a4e6fa"}, "3": {"node_id": "5aa7bbab-e4a0-4650-a774-ab98cdb6a3a9", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/id/resources/grey-literature/pedoman-metode-evaluasi-kes